\vect E=E_{0}\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}i^{n}\frac{2n+1}{n(n+1)}\left(\vect M_{o1n}^{(1)}-i\vect N_{e1n}^{(1)}\right),
\]

\end_inset

where the even/odd VSWF and 
\begin_inset Formula $m\ge0$
\end_inset

 convention is used.)
